title: When you are juking your ass off.
body:
https://j.gifs.com/g5q2gk.gif

And your fed teammate kills the person you were running from.

replies.body: Daaang, Urf saved {{champion:6}} from {{champion:161}}!!! What a play.
The octopus did not attack the crab's weak point for massive damage.
It's always the eyes! Why didn't it follow the rule?
When {{champion:161}} is chasing {{champion:6}} with tunnel vision and gets one-shot by Fisherman {{champion:105}} ult

Bruh one time I was behind as Twitch so I started split pushing bot while everybody else team fought mid and this poor Rek'Sai kept trying to game me but every time I finished a wave I q'd out plus she got minion blocked. One time I guess she caught me in her Tremor Sense and chased me through river but she just got jumped on by my team RIP
It's a good thing he missed all the grabs vital organs.
